OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774015868
OL,3,CConcerns as Sark spends #30,000 on
OL,4,Csecond future survey since 2024
OL,6,FThe Seigneur of Sark says the island
OL,7,Fcould be embroiled in an 'endless
OL,8,Fcycle' of projects to determine its
OL,9,Ffuture, as the government sets out yet
OL,10,Fanother new initiative.
OL,12,F'Future Sark' is the second survey
OL,13,Fassessing the island's future
OL,14,Fpriorities in three years, following a
OL,15,Fseries of recommendations compiled in
OL,16,Fthe Prince's Foundation - now the
OL,17,FKing's Foundation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774015868
OL,3,CConcerns as Sark spends #30,000 on
OL,4,Csecond future survey since 2024
OL,6,FMajor Christopher Beaumont, Sark's
OL,7,F23rd Seigneur, worked closely to
OL,8,Fcomplete that report, which undertook
OL,9,Fextensive community work to discover
OL,10,Fresidents' priorities.
OL,12,FThe Prince's Foundation report was
OL,13,Fpublished in 2024, with the Seigneur
OL,14,Fnow concerned that Future Sark could
OL,15,Fbe another in a long list of projects
OL,16,Flooking to create a long-term plan for
OL,17,Fthe island.
OL,19,F"I think the community feels it
OL,20,Falready knows what it wants," the
OL,21,FSeigneur told ITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774015868
OL,3,CConcerns as Sark spends #30,000 on
OL,4,Csecond future survey since 2024
OL,6,F"There is a danger of continuing to
OL,7,Fcome up with a plan, failing to
OL,8,Fdeliver, and then having to come up
OL,9,Fwith another plan, so you're in an
OL,10,Fendless cycle."
OL,12,FFuture Sark, unlike the previous
OL,13,Freport, is being conducted by Sark's
OL,14,FChief Pleas, which is entering only
OL,15,Fits 16th year as a democracy.
OL,17,FThe project has been costed at
OL,18,F#30,000, and will use the consultancy
OL,19,Ffirm Question Factory to survey the
OL,20,Fisland's interests.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774015868
OL,3,CConcerns as Sark spends #30,000 on
OL,4,Csecond future survey since 2024
OL,6,FOpponents to Future Sark believe this
OL,7,Fmoney would be better spent fulfilling
OL,8,Fthe recommendations of the previous
OL,9,F2024 report.
OL,11,FHowever, Natalie Tighe, a Conseiller
OL,12,Fin Sark's Chief Pleas, insists the new
OL,13,Fsurvey is necessary.
OL,15,F"Sark is still relatively young as a
OL,16,Fdemocracy," Conseiller Tighe told ITV
OL,17,FNews.
OL,19,F"We've had the Krone report, the
OL,20,FJelicot report, the Knifeton report
OL,21,Fand the Prince's Foundation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774015868
OL,3,CConcerns as Sark spends #30,000 on
OL,4,Csecond future survey since 2024
OL,6,F"We're looking to build on these with
OL,7,FFuture Sark, to strengthen them, and
OL,8,Fbuild a roadmap for the future."
OL,10,FFuture Sark began with a presentation
OL,11,Ffrom Guernsey's Lieutenant Governor in
OL,12,Fthe Island Hall - which the Seigneur
OL,13,Fattended - and will run throughout the
OL,14,Fspring and summer of 2026.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
